1
00:01:24,820 --> 00:01:29,880
[Youthful Glory]

2
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:32,910
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:37,200
I appreciate your kindness, Xu.

4
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:40,650
However, as we are traveling far to Lingzhou,

5
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,580
official matters take priority.

6
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:44,280
There's no need to delay our journey

7
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,740
for such trivial matters.

8
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:51,080
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

9
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:53,580
Your Highness,

10
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:56,039
which carriage should I put the luggage in?

11
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:56,920
Yun Yi,

12
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,979
I have something else to tell you.

13
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,760
Mr. Fu,

14
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:08,320
I have some matters

15
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,360
to consult with you about.

16
00:02:08,889 --> 00:02:13,120
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

17
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:11,140
Could I borrow you for a while?

18
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,200
Sure.

19
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,200
After you, Second Young Master Shu.

20
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:22,010
Tan, are you sure you only want to keep two carriages?

21
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:22,960
Once you depart from the capital,

22
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:25,079
it will be too late to add more.

23
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,360
Xu, your kindness is overwhelming.

24
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,220
I do not deserve such generosity.

25
00:02:37,690 --> 00:02:38,490
Chai Gui,

26
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,240
after simplifying the luggage,

27
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,970
put everything in one carriage

28
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,500
and keep another one for passengers.

29
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,360
Yes.

30
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,770
Don't worry. Every few days,

31
00:02:57,790 --> 00:02:58,810
I will write back

32
00:02:58,829 --> 00:03:00,200
to let you know I'm safe.

33
00:03:00,670 --> 00:03:02,240
I will eagerly await your letters every day.

34
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,520
You must keep your word.

35
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,080
Also, Tan,

36
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:08,160
if you hear any news about Zhang Huaiyu,

37
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,320
you must let me know.

38
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,760
Madam Yun, on this journey,

39
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,920
you're the only one by Her Highness's side.

40
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:18,120
You must take good care of Her Highness.

41
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,360
Is Miss Yun

42
00:03:20,070 --> 00:03:21,760
really Qizhi's concubine?

43
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:24,680
Don't worry.

44
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,640
Wherever I am, Her Highness is too.

45
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,790
Jingran, what's your opinion?

46
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,370
I wouldn't dare.

47
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:33,280
I've just never heard you mention her before.

48
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:34,920
It seems to me

49
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:37,270
she and Her Highness are quite close.

50
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:39,270
Her Highness doesn't seem to mind.

51
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,880
Tan doesn't mind,

52
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,360
but I think you

53
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,800
seem quite concerned.

54
00:03:43,820 --> 00:03:44,680
I...

55
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:48,480
Alright, you can all go back now.

56
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,320
With all of you waiting for me,

57
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,720
I'll surely return soon.

58
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:52,079
Let's go.

59
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,000
Depart!

60
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:15,360
After Ming Tingyuan's death,

61
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,320
the Haiyou Sect has been keeping a close watch

62
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,080
on the Prince of Dingbei's Mansion,

63
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:18,800
but they haven't noticed

64
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,060
any unusual activity.

65
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:23,680
As for Ming Tingyuan's death,

66
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,210
perhaps I'm overthinking,

67
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,750
but Prince of Dingbei's trip to Lingzhou

68
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:29,350
will surely stir up trouble.

69
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,760
He is tough

70
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,460
and doesn't play by the rules.

71
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:35,320
Even though the Su family is fully prepared,

72
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:37,850
they might still find it difficult to handle.

73
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:39,880
Therefore, the Chancellor's intention

74
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:42,010
is for the Prince of Dingbei's journey

75
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,920
to be a one-way trip.

76
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,500
Rest assured, My Lord.

77
00:05:45,670 --> 00:05:47,880
I've already sent people to monitor along the way,

78
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:50,530
and we'll act when the time is right.

79
00:05:50,850 --> 00:05:53,000
Prince of Dingbei is traveling with the Princess Consort,

80
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,400
so he won't be unguarded.

81
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:58,340
The assassination must not alert them in advance.

82
00:05:58,670 --> 00:06:00,330
Have someone keep an eye on it.

83
00:06:00,590 --> 00:06:02,520
Wait for the Chancellor's orders.

84
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,600
Plan everything carefully before taking action.

85
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:29,220
Madam Yun, when did you enter the Prince's mansion?

86
00:06:30,670 --> 00:06:31,640
Two months ago.

87
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:36,480
What do you usually do

88
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,120
in the Prince's mansion?

89
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,610
Protect the Princess Consort.

90
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:45,880
Is it so difficult to be a concubine these days?

91
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,560
So you only protect the Princess Consort

92
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,000
and don't need to take care of the Prince?

93
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:54,260
The Prince has Zhuiying take care of him.

94
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,560
So your role in the Prince's mansion

95
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,320
is actually the same as Zhuiying's,

96
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,800
only needing to ensure the Princess Consort's safety,

97
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,680
nothing more?

98
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,300
Are you a member of the Jinyun Guards?

99
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,760
Then,

100
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,560
what's your rank among the Jinyun Guards?

101
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,420
Is your martial skill top-notch?

102
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,560
I'm sure your skills

103
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,660
must be extraordinary.

104
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:20,860
I admire you from the bottom of my heart.

105
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:23,120
Her Highness mentioned that you

106
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,200
are the most handsome man in the capital,

107
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,700
but she didn't mention that your questions

108
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:29,030
are also the most numerous in the capital.

109
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,760
It's the height of summer.

110
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:35,420
Sour plum soup can relieve the heat and fatigue.

111
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:49,990
It's so refreshingly cool.

112
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,440
The cheese pastries from Changping Market

113
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,880
and the candied fruits from Sanliu Restaurant

114
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,560
are all your usual favorites.

115
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,890
Tan,

116
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,760
are you still blaming me

117
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,330
for your father's case?

118
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,159
Do you truly want to know?

119
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,919
The one who framed the Ming family and my father

120
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,320
wasn't you.

121
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,800
So why would I blame you?

122
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:50,040
It's just that I have some doubts

123
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,720
that remain unresolved.

124
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,400
During this time,

125
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,660
I haven't received an explanation from you.

126
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,730
Since you've brought it up,

127
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,650
I'll speak frankly.

128
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,920
When news of my father's ineffective disaster relief

129
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,120
reached the capital,

130
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,840
why did you immediately

131
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:10,680
lead the Imperial Guards to seal off the Ming's Mansion?

132
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:13,350
I was merely following orders.

133
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:16,720
Did the orders come from His Majesty

134
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,280
or His Highness?

135
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:35,050
When Zixuan was escorting my father back to the capital,

136
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,200
why did you

137
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,920
have the Dingbei Army secretly release my father?

138
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:39,920
Wouldn't this

139
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:42,040
confirm that my father was fleeing from guilt,

140
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,680
framing him as dishonorable?

141
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:45,280
It was the Prince of Dingbei who volunteered

142
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:47,610
to escort your father back to the capital.

143
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:48,920
Do you know

144
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,200
who truly wants your father dead?

145
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,840
It's your husband, the Prince of Dingbei.

146
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,450
Why are you keeping silent, Xu?

147
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:10,920
Is it that you can't say it, don't want to say it,

148
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,560
or don't dare to?

149
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,720
Lu Ting is one of us.

150
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:29,200
He led the Imperial Guards to seal off the place

151
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:29,840
because we didn't want

152
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,280
any villains to take advantage of the situation

153
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:32,840
and frame your father.

154
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:34,810
I just didn't expect

155
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,320
that they would plant the evidence

156
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,200
in the Ming family's ancestral home.

157
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,280
That soldier accepted a bribe

158
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,340
and was bought off.

159
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,160
I anticipated that the other party

160
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,720
would definitely make a move during the journey,

161
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:45,180
so I had Shen Yu take precautions in advance.

162
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:47,080
However, in the end, the one we caught

163
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,810
was a soldier from our own army.

164
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,360
I have one more question.

165
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:57,920
That day in prison,

166
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,520
why did you try so hard to prevent me

167
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,520
from seeing my father one last time?

168
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,400
Father!

169
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,320
I know

170
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:08,160
there was no way to change the outcome of the case.

171
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,320
All I wanted

172
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,800
was to see my father

173
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:12,460
and send him off one last time.

174
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:14,720
Open your eyes and take a look.

175
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,400
Father.

176
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,160
Father!

177
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:18,680
I came too late.

178
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,160
I understand that you were

179
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,320
too busy to arrange it.

180
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,380
But that day, I was already in prison.

181
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,920
If you hadn't interfered,

182
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:28,960
I would have been able to see my father

183
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,800
one last time.

184
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,210
After leaving the capital,

185
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:49,520
were we followed?

186
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,440
There are three people.

187
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,200
Don't worry, Sir.

188
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,280
The secret guards are watching them. They haven't been alerted.

189
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,340
Stop the carriage!

190
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,080
Get off the horse.

191
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,400
Jiang Qizhi, you asked me to speak frankly.

192
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,800
But when I did, you ran away.

193
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:10,660
Is this how you show your willingness to reconcile?

194
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,800
We've only been out of the capital for half a day,

195
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:14,200
and this is how you treat me.

196
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,960
How can we talk about marital affection in the future?

197
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,600
Get down.

198
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,100
Where are we going?

199
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,680
To find medicine that can cure your heartache.

200
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,280
I won't go.

201
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,380
You don't have a choice today.

202
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:33,200
Jiang Qizhi, put me down!

203
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,610
You guys go ahead first.

204
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:39,140
Meet at Shaxi in Suicheng.

205
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:40,980
Well...

206
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:08,400
Get off the horse.

207
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,860
Some people are following us.

208
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:19,920
Let's go.

209
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:34,280
There really are a few people.

210
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:34,810
Let's go.

211
00:13:35,330 --> 00:13:36,660
Where are you taking me?

212
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,380
You'll know when we get there.

213
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,080
Where are we?

214
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,560
Why did you bring me here?

215
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:23,340
♪ My destined fate in this life ♪

216
00:14:24,110 --> 00:14:27,430
♪ Echoes in your heartbeat ♪

217
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:31,170
♪ Flowing through the lines of your palm ♪

218
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:34,870
♪ A heart in bridal red ♪

219
00:14:35,830 --> 00:14:39,460
♪ At peace beneath the lanterns ♪

220
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:43,350
♪ Counting the years as we wait ♪

221
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:47,160
♪ Waiting for black hair to turn white ♪

222
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,200
Tan.

223
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:50,710
♪ As you're by my side ♪

224
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:59,750
♪ Never thought I'd turn back
and see us tied by a red string ♪

225
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:54,800
Tan.

226
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:57,520
Father.

227
00:15:00,470 --> 00:15:07,700
♪ The weight of family,
my hand in yours ♪

228
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:12,600
♪ Destiny ends in companionship ♪

229
00:15:12,860 --> 00:15:16,270
♪ With my wish fulfilled at last ♪

230
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,080
As for you,

231
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:17,870
this may look like a dead end.

232
00:15:16,760 --> 00:15:22,460
♪ Now I always have someone to long for ♪

233
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,720
But

234
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:22,920
it is not the end.

235
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:27,080
With our backs against the wall, we can turn the tables.

236
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:29,620
♪ Even rooftops remember
each moonlit night ♪

237
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:29,650
You still have a chance to survive.

238
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,800
It just requires taking some risks.

239
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,460
Before 1 a.m. tonight,

240
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,600
Yu's convoy must leave the capital.

241
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:54,260
Depart, right away!

242
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:56,920
I must return as soon as possible.

243
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:57,620
[Capital]

244
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,520
So that day in prison,

245
00:16:10,520 --> 00:16:11,980
everything that happened

246
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,720
was all planned by Xu in advance.

247
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:15,520
Yes.

248
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,840
Then why didn't he tell me?

249
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:21,680
He didn't mention a word even afterward.

250
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,080
Tan,

251
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:28,720
this is a crime of deceiving the emperor.

252
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:29,960
If there's the slightest mistake,

253
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,420
all those who know about it

254
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:32,920
will be punished by death.

255
00:16:34,920 --> 00:16:36,280
His Highness did this

256
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:38,080
for your sake as well.

257
00:16:43,040 --> 00:16:44,970
Chancellor Su is very suspicious.

258
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:47,320
Even if I die in front of him,

259
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,680
he'll still send people

260
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:53,050
to keep a close watch on the Prince's mansion.

261
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,440
This isn't over yet.

262
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,720
I swear I'll do everything in my power to find a way.

263
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:00,960
Don't worry, Tan.

264
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:03,540
I'll take care of everything.

265
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:07,839
I misunderstood my husband.

266
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:12,520
If I didn't bring her here soon

267
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:13,579
to meet her father,

268
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:15,079
I'm afraid she would be

269
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:16,940
unhappy throughout the journey.

270
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:18,240
What's more worrying is

271
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:18,839
she might

272
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:20,700
hold a grudge against me for life.

273
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:21,839
Xu.

274
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,800
Alright.

275
00:17:27,800 --> 00:17:28,840
Have a seat.

276
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,690
The soup will be ready soon.

277
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:36,800
I know

278
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:39,320
you did this for my own good.

279
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,090
But we are husband and wife.

280
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:44,000
If you can bear such a heavy burden

281
