This time, I have a few requirements

564
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:40,800
that must be included.

565
00:32:41,490 --> 00:32:44,320
What are your requirements?

566
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:45,080
First,

567
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:47,380
no matter what happens in the future,

568
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:50,040
we must be honest with each other

569
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,320
and not hide anything.

570
00:32:52,320 --> 00:32:53,040
Second,

571
00:32:53,040 --> 00:32:54,440
no matter how mad you get,

572
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:56,090
you can't just ignore me

573
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:58,640
or treat me as if I don't exist.

574
00:32:59,320 --> 00:32:59,880
Third...

575
00:33:00,070 --> 00:33:02,530
Who goes around making contracts like that?

576
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:05,000
I know I was wrong.

577
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,240
Please be magnanimous

578
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:08,280
and forgive me this once.

579
00:33:12,340 --> 00:33:13,520
Besides,

580
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:14,840
ignorance is no crime.

581
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:16,080
If you hadn't

582
00:33:16,080 --> 00:33:17,160
kept everything from me,

583
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:19,160
how could I have misunderstood you?

584
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,160
After all,

585
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:21,760
it's still your fault.

586
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,020
Moreover, the contract is torn, so be it.

587
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:29,320
Don't tell me you want to have

588
00:33:29,320 --> 00:33:31,650
a lifelong contractual marriage with me.

589
00:33:31,760 --> 00:33:33,800
Now that you're fond of me,

590
00:33:33,800 --> 00:33:35,840
and I admire you,

591
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,900
what do we need a contract for?

592
00:33:39,950 --> 00:33:42,160
You've got a point.

593
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:50,040
Eat more, get fatter.

594
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:53,040
Get fatter, taste better.

595
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,760
Get fatter.

596
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:57,800
Get fatter, taste better.

597
00:33:58,320 --> 00:34:00,840
Eat more.

598
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,159
Miss Yun.

599
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:13,650
It's been two days already.

600
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:16,520
Can Zhuiying find this place?

601
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:17,630
Questioning the Jinyun Guards

602
00:34:17,630 --> 00:34:19,199
is the same as questioning the master.

603
00:34:19,199 --> 00:34:20,860
You don't trust His Highness?

604
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,880
Miss Yun, I absolutely didn't mean that.

605
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:27,969
I just couldn't help asking

606
00:34:27,969 --> 00:34:29,199
because I was a bit worried.

607
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:30,639
What's the use of worrying?

608
00:34:30,639 --> 00:34:31,239
Will Zhuiying

609
00:34:31,239 --> 00:34:33,900
come back earlier just because you're worried?

610
00:34:34,159 --> 00:34:34,719
Well...

611
00:34:35,719 --> 00:34:36,400
Miss,

612
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:38,940
I've already fed the chickens this morning.

613
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:41,639
They're still too skinny. Feed them a bit more.

614
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:42,880
Alright.

615
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:47,040
Madam,

616
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:48,639
may I buy one of your chickens?

617
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:50,080
Sure, I'm raising these chickens

618
00:34:50,080 --> 00:34:51,840
to sell anyway.

619
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:52,400
However,

620
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:54,199
you'll have to do it yourselves.

621
00:34:54,790 --> 00:34:55,400
Our...

622
00:34:57,160 --> 00:34:58,000
Ourselves?

623
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:02,760
Miss Yun!

624
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:04,360
It's alright. I'll do it.

625
00:35:06,510 --> 00:35:07,000
Here.

626
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:36,560
What's the use of being educated

627
00:36:37,020 --> 00:36:38,760
if I can't even deal with a chicken?

628
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:40,490
Isn't this what you always call

629
00:36:40,780 --> 00:36:43,040
"as weak as a kitten"?

630
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:53,880
Miss Yun, you certainly make it look effortless.

631
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,480
This chicken's good at

632
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:57,560
reading the room.

633
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:59,600
Chickens don't understand human reasoning.

634
00:36:59,600 --> 00:37:01,520
But it's not much different from facing an enemy.

635
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:03,520
When facing a tough opponent, keeping your presence is key.

636
00:37:03,520 --> 00:37:04,600
If you lose your composure

637
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:05,800
in front of the enemy,

638
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:07,560
you naturally can't win.

639
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,280
Losing is fine, but don't lose your pride.

640
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:11,880
Miss Yun, you've got a point.

641
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:14,560
So, Miss Yun, are you suggesting that

642
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:15,720
my presence

643
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:17,680
is inferior to that of this chicken?

644
00:37:17,680 --> 00:37:18,140
Indeed.

645
00:37:30,720 --> 00:37:32,240
Smells really good, huh?

646
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:35,480
You couldn't even catch a chicken.

647
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:38,280
How could you have such skill in roasting chicken?

648
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:38,960
Every time

649
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,560
you eat roast chicken,

650
00:37:40,560 --> 00:37:41,640
you look like you're loving it.

651
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:42,720
So I became interested

652
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:45,180
and specially learned from the chef at home.

653
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:47,080
But I don't know how it tastes.

654
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:47,760
I hope

655
00:37:47,780 --> 00:37:49,040
it suits your taste.

656
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:49,960
It does.

657
00:37:51,160 --> 00:37:52,360
It smells very good.

658
00:37:56,640 --> 00:37:57,300
It's ready.

659
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:11,690
Here you are.

660
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:29,610
Here, there's another one.

661
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:31,720
You bought this chicken

662
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:33,050
and cooked it yourself.

663
00:38:33,080 --> 00:38:34,410
You should eat some too.

664
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:36,480
No need to give me all the best parts.

665
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:39,400
Miss Yun,

666
00:38:39,960 --> 00:38:40,890
I specially made

667
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:43,160
this roast chicken for you.

668
00:38:52,300 --> 00:38:53,280
I mean,

669
00:38:54,160 --> 00:38:55,360
few people

670
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:57,460
can enjoy their food as much as you do.

671
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:59,420
It's like no delicacy in the world

672
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:02,340
can match the roast chicken you're holding.

673
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:10,600
Honestly, nothing can compare.

674
00:39:11,740 --> 00:39:13,560
Your roast chicken

675
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:15,120
could easily rank

676
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,800
second best in the world.

677
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:23,120
Miss Yun, then in your heart,

678
00:39:23,240 --> 00:39:24,720
is the best roast chicken

679
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:26,520
made by His Highness?

680
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:28,680
When I was young, food was scarce.

681
00:39:28,680 --> 00:39:30,080
I went hungry for days on end.

682
00:39:30,080 --> 00:39:31,880
It was His Highness's roast chicken

683
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:32,940
that kept me alive.

684
00:39:41,890 --> 00:39:42,490
By the way,

685
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:44,800
why did we come here?

686
00:39:45,280 --> 00:39:46,440
Could it be

687
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:49,280
that your household chef's secret recipe

688
00:39:49,390 --> 00:39:51,760
needs a special setting?

689
00:39:54,820 --> 00:39:55,600
Follow me.

690
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:25,810
♪ A quiet wish born in the dark ♪

691
00:40:26,690 --> 00:40:29,930
♪ Will it reach someone's ears at all? ♪

692
00:40:30,660 --> 00:40:34,350
♪ A fleeting brush in a passing glance ♪

693
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:38,450
♪ Etching longing deep within ♪

694
00:40:39,540 --> 00:40:42,940
♪ You are the flame ♪

695
00:40:43,590 --> 00:40:47,140
♪ That lights my endless night ♪

696
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:52,650
♪ Because of the resolve
we see in each other's eyes ♪

697
00:40:54,690 --> 00:40:57,730
♪ We believe in forever ♪

698
00:40:59,690 --> 00:41:03,900
♪ May the fleeting years
gather into points of light ♪

699
00:41:04,190 --> 00:41:07,530
♪ Hold on to this bond year after year ♪

700
00:41:07,870 --> 00:41:12,030
♪ Side by side through endless tales ♪

701
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:16,190
♪ Love rests deep in heart and eyes ♪

702
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:20,020
♪ May the fleeting years gather into light,
and you are that point of light ♪

703
00:41:20,410 --> 00:41:23,780
♪ Time flows in silence,
through lingering nights ♪

704
00:41:24,520 --> 00:41:28,610
♪ Like stars in the long night ♪

705
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:32,280
♪ Through all the changes, near or far ♪

706
00:41:32,770 --> 00:41:38,820
♪ I'll be with you
to enjoy the unfinished story ♪

707
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:08,850
Where exactly are we going?

708
00:42:08,910 --> 00:42:09,720
Hurry up!

709
00:42:09,720 --> 00:42:11,180
We're running out of time!

710
00:42:11,600 --> 00:42:13,840
No, I can't run anymore.

711
00:42:13,940 --> 00:42:16,340
Hurry up, we're really running out of time.

712
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:17,520
Hey,

713
00:42:17,720 --> 00:42:19,320
could it be Father and Mother

714
00:42:19,690 --> 00:42:20,760
planning something special

715
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,120
to surprise me?

716
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:24,080
I wasn't aware of that.

717
00:42:24,460 --> 00:42:26,320
Could it be that Her Highness arranged something special for you

718
00:42:26,320 --> 00:42:27,920
before leaving the capital?

719
00:42:29,120 --> 00:42:30,780
That can't be the case either.

720
00:42:32,710 --> 00:42:33,600
Hey little one,

721
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:35,160
if you don't tell me clearly where we're going,

722
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:36,040
I won't go.

723
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,680
That person said if you don't go,

724
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:40,400
you'll regret it for life.

725
00:42:41,080 --> 00:42:42,530
I don't even know

726
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:43,400
who that person is.

727
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:44,560
What if I encounter bad people?

728
00:42:44,560 --> 00:42:46,490
Then I'll truly regret it for life.

729
00:42:47,600 --> 00:42:48,640
What do you have that's worth

730
00:42:48,640 --> 00:42:50,300
being targeted by bad people?

731
00:42:54,600 --> 00:42:55,130
Let's go.

732
00:42:55,160 --> 00:42:55,760
Don't go!

733
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:56,520
You're such a grown-up.

734
00:42:56,520 --> 00:42:57,640
Why are you still acting like a child,

735
00:42:57,640 --> 00:42:58,770
throwing a tantrum?

736
00:42:59,640 --> 00:43:01,120
I act like a child?

737
00:43:01,120 --> 00:43:02,280
Then what do you act like?

738
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:03,480
An old grandpa.

739
00:43:03,730 --> 00:43:05,560
Let's go. We're almost there.

740
00:43:09,880 --> 00:43:10,640
Here it is.

741
00:43:13,560 --> 00:43:16,220
Little brat, where's the person you mentioned?

742
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:16,840
I...

743
00:43:19,440 --> 00:43:20,000
Fireworks are being set off!

744
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:20,640
Look!

745
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:22,240
It's starting!

746
00:43:22,240 --> 00:43:22,680
Come quickly!

747
00:43:22,680 --> 00:43:23,360
Fireworks are going off!

748
00:43:22,790 --> 00:43:26,300
[Suiting All Tastes]

749
00:43:24,080 --> 00:43:25,520
It's so beautiful. Hurry up!

750
00:43:25,520 --> 00:43:25,840
It's starting!

751
00:43:25,840 --> 00:43:27,360
Come over.

752
00:43:28,160 --> 00:43:30,720
This young lady is quite something.

753
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:32,830
[Suiting All Tastes]

754
00:43:30,720 --> 00:43:33,080
Her courage stretches as wide as the sky.

755
00:43:34,600 --> 00:43:36,440
If you want to cause trouble, bother someone else.

756
00:43:36,440 --> 00:43:37,720
Why waste it on me?
